{
  "name": "FarmaBot Pro - Workflow Principal",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "webhook/whatsapp",
        "responseMode": "responseNode",
        "options": {
          "domainWhitelist": "*.whatsapp.com"
        }
      },
      "name": "WhatsApp Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [250, 300],
      "id": "webhook-whatsapp"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "runOnceForEachItem",
        "jsCode": "// Validar e extrair dados da mensagem WhatsApp\nconst body = $input.item.json.body;\n\nif (!body.entry?.[0]?.changes?.[0]?.value?.messages?.[0]) {\n  return { error: 'Mensagem inv√°lida' };\n}\n\nconst message = body.entry[0].changes[0].value.messages[0];\nconst contact = body.entry[0].changes[0].value.contacts[0];\n\nreturn {\n  messageId: message.id,\n  from: message.from,\n  type: message.type,\n  text: message.text?.body || '',\n  timestamp: message.timestamp,\n  contactName: contact.profile.name,\n  isValid: true\n};"
      },
      "name": "Processar Mensagem",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [450, 300],
      "id": "process-message"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": false
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "value1": "={{$json.text}}",
              "operation": "contains",
              "value2": "pre√ßo"
            },
            {
              "value1": "={{$json.text}}",
              "operation": "contains", 
              "value2": "valor"
            },
            {
              "value1": "={{$json.text}}",
              "operation": "contains",
              "value2": "quanto custa"
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "or"
        }
      },
      "name": "√â Consulta de Pre√ßo?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [650, 300],
      "id": "check-price-query"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "database",
        "operation": "select",
        "schema": "public",
        "table": "produtos",
        "returnAll": true,
        "where": {
          "condition": "AND",
          "values": [
            {
              "column": "nome",
              "operator": "like",
              "value": "={{$json.searchTerm}}%"
            },
            {
              "column": "ativo",
              "value": true
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "Buscar no Supabase",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [850, 200],
      "id": "supabase-search"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "={{$env.ERP_API_URL}}/api/produtos/consulta",
        "authentication": "predefinedCredentialType",
        "nodeCredentialType": "httpBasicAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "termo",
              "value": "={{$json.searchTerm}}"
            },
            {
              "name": "loja_id",
              "value": "={{$env.LOJA_ID}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "timeout": 10000
        }
      },
      "name": "Consultar ERP",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [850, 400],
      "id": "erp-query"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "Voc√™ √© um assistente de farm√°cia prestativo e profissional. Responda de forma clara, educada e objetiva. Use emojis com modera√ß√£o. Sempre forne√ßa informa√ß√µes precisas sobre produtos e pre√ßos."
            },
            {
              "role": "user", 
              "content": "={{$json.originalMessage}}"
            },
            {
              "role": "assistant",
              "content": "Encontrei os seguintes produtos:\n{{$json.formattedProducts}}\n\nPosso ajudar com mais alguma coisa? üòä"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.7,
          "maxTokens": 300
        }
      },
      "name": "Formatar Resposta AI",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1050, 300],
      "id": "format-ai-response"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "message",
        "operation": "sendText",
        "phoneNumberId": "={{$env.WHATSAPP_PHONE_ID}}",
        "to": "={{$json.from}}",
        "text": "={{$json.response}}",
        "options": {
          "preview_url": false
        }
      },
      "name": "Enviar Resposta WhatsApp",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.whatsapp",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1250, 300],
      "id": "send-whatsapp"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## FarmaBot Pro - Fluxo Principal\n\nEste workflow processa mensagens do WhatsApp e:\n1. Valida e extrai dados\n2. Identifica inten√ß√£o (pre√ßo, estoque, pedido)\n3. Consulta dados (Supabase + ERP)\n4. Formata resposta com AI\n5. Envia resposta ao cliente\n\n### Configura√ß√µes Necess√°rias:\n- WhatsApp Business API Token\n- Supabase Credentials\n- ERP API Credentials\n- OpenAI API Key",
        "height": 400
      },
      "name": "Documenta√ß√£o",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [250, 50],
      "id": "documentation"
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
